			<td colspan="6" class="DetailTitle" style="text-align:center;">
                            Summary on Grant Application Form</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td colspan="6" class="DetailValue" style="padding:5px;">
                        <span id="lblAbstract">The condensed matter laser physics programme will be conducted at FELIX by 11 university groups under the overall coordination of Professor C.R. Pidgeon (Heriot-Watt University, HW) along the following research strands (see CASE FOR SUPPORT, PART 3 - Diagrammatic Project Plan): 1) NL inter-subband and inter-sublevel excitation of low-dimensional systems(LDS); 2) NL interband dynamics of narrow gap semiconductors; 3) device applications; 4) NL and high field magnetooptics, organics and superconductivity.</span>
                        </td>
		</tr>
